        <updateDate>2021-06-14T16:54:43Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Estate Tax Rate Reduction Act </b></p> <p>This bill reduces the rate for the tax on estates, gifts, and generation-skipping transfers to 20%. (Under current law, the highest rate is 40%.) </p> <p>The bill also exempts the budgetary effects of the tax reduction from the Pay-As-You-Go (PAYGO) rules established by the Statutory Pay-As-You-Go Act of 2010 and the FY2018 congressional budget resolution.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
